#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:1
msgid "核心概念速览"
msgstr "Core Concepts at a Glance"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:3
msgid ""
"本章用表格和简短说明梳理 qteasy 中的核心概念，便于在阅读后续章节或使用 API 时"
"快速查阅。更完整的结构与关系见 [总体架构与设计思路](00-overview.md)。"
msgstr ""
"This chapter organizes the core concepts in qteasy in tables and brief notes, "
"making it easy to quickly look them up when reading subsequent chapters or "
"using the API. For a more complete structure and relationships, see [Overall "
"Architecture and Design Approach](00-overview.md)."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:5
msgid "1. 概念表（名称 / 含义 / 在文档中的位置）"
msgstr "1. Concept Table (Name / Meaning / Location in the Document)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "概念"
msgstr "Concepts"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "含义"
msgstr "Meaning"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "本系列中的位置"
msgstr "Where It Fits in This Series"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**DataSource**"
msgstr "**DataSource**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "本地数据存储的抽象，管理文件或数据库中的历史数据表，不主动拉取数据"
msgstr ""
"An abstraction of local data storage that manages historical data tables in "
"files or databases, and does not proactively pull data."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "[数据获取、存储与数据类型](02-data-layer.md)"
msgstr "[Data Acquisition, Storage, and Data Types](02-data-layer.md)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**数据表**"
msgstr "**Data Table**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "DataSource 中的表，按统一结构存储行情、财务、宏观等数据"
msgstr ""
"Tables in the DataSource that store market, financial, macro, and other data "
"in a unified structure."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**DataType**"
msgstr "**DataType**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "“策略可引用的信息”的类型描述，由 name、freq、asset_type 等确定"
msgstr ""
"A type description of “information that a strategy can reference,” determined "
"by name, freq, asset_type, etc."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid ""
"[数据获取、存储与数据类型](02-data-layer.md)、[策略如何声明与使用数据](03-"
"data-in-strategies.md)"
msgstr ""
"[Data Retrieval, Storage, and Data Types](02-data-layer.md), [How Strategies "
"Declare and Use Data](03-data-in-strategies.md)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**htype**"
msgstr "**htype**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid ""
"历史数据类型名称（如 close、open），常与 freq、asset_type 一起用来标识一种数据"
msgstr ""
"Historical data type name (e.g., close, open), often used together with freq "
"and asset_type to identify a kind of data"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**dtype_id**"
msgstr "**dtype_id**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "DataType 的唯一标识，形如 `name_assettype_freq`（如 `close_E_d`）"
msgstr ""
"The unique identifier of a DataType, in the form `name_assettype_freq` (e.g., "
"`close_E_d`)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "下文“dtype_id 的构成与示例”"
msgstr "See “Composition and Examples of dtype_id” below."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**Operator**"
msgstr "**Operator**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid ""
"策略容器与运行入口，持有 Group 列表与 group_timing_table，提供 run(config)"
msgstr ""
"The strategy container and execution entry point; holds a list of Groups and "
"the group_timing_table, and provides run(config)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "[Operator 与 Group](04-operator-and-groups.md)"
msgstr "[Operator and Group](04-operator-and-groups.md)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**Group**"
msgstr "**Group**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "具有相同 run_freq、run_timing 的策略集合，拥有 signal_type 与 blender"
msgstr ""
"A collection of strategies with the same run_freq and run_timing, with a "
"signal_type and a blender"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**Strategy**"
msgstr "**Strategy**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid ""
"策略基类及其子类，声明 data_types/window_length、Parameter，实现 realize()"
msgstr ""
"The base Strategy class and its subclasses; declares data_types/window_length "
"and Parameters, and implements realize()"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "[Strategy 如何运行](05-strategy-lifecycle.md)"
msgstr "[How a Strategy Runs](05-strategy-lifecycle.md)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**run_freq**"
msgstr "**run_freq**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "策略（组）的运行频率，如 `'d'` 日、`'m'` 月"
msgstr ""
"The execution frequency of a strategy (group), e.g., `'d'` for daily, `'m'` "
"for monthly."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**run_timing**"
msgstr "**run_timing**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "策略（组）在周期内的运行时机，如 `'close'` 收盘、`'open'` 开盘"
msgstr ""
"When a strategy (group) runs within a period, e.g., `'close'` at close, "
"`'open'` at open."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**group_timing_table**"
msgstr "**group_timing_table**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "时间步 × Group 的表，标记每个时间步哪些 Group 运行"
msgstr ""
"A Time Step × Group table that marks which Groups run at each time step."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**blender**"
msgstr "**blender**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "同 Group 内多策略信号的混合方式（表达式或默认规则）"
msgstr ""
"How signals from multiple strategies within the same Group are combined "
"(expression or default rules)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**signal_type**"
msgstr "**signal_type**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "信号类型：PT（目标仓位）、PS（比例买卖）、VS（数量买卖）"
msgstr ""
"Signal types: PT (target position), PS (proportional buy/sell), VS (quantity "
"buy/sell)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "下文“三种信号类型 PT/PS/VS”"
msgstr "Below: “Three signal types PT/PS/VS”"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**Parameter**"
msgstr "**Parameter**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "策略可调参数的定义（名称、类型、取值范围等）"
msgstr ""
"Definition of strategy tunable parameters (name, type, value range, etc.)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**data_types**"
msgstr "**data_types**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "策略声明的所需数据类型（DataType 或列表）"
msgstr "Required data types declared by the strategy (DataType or list)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "[策略如何声明与使用数据](03-data-in-strategies.md)"
msgstr "[How a strategy declares and uses data](03-data-in-strategies.md)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**window_length**"
msgstr "**window_length**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "策略所需历史数据的窗口长度（如 20 天）"
msgstr ""
"Window length of historical data required by the strategy (e.g., 20 days)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**realize()**"
msgstr "**realize()**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "策略逻辑入口，无参数，通过 get_pars/get_data 取数并返回信号"
msgstr ""
"Strategy logic entry point; takes no parameters; fetches data via get_pars/"
"get_data and returns signals"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**get_data / get_pars**"
msgstr "**get_data / get_pars**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "在 realize() 内按 dtype_id 取数据、按参数名取可调参数"
msgstr ""
"Within realize(), fetch data by dtype_id and fetch tunable parameters by "
"parameter name"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**Backtester**"
msgstr "**Backtester**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "回测执行器，按 group_timing_table 驱动 Operator 并模拟成交"
msgstr ""
"Backtest executor: drives the Operator according to group_timing_table and "
"simulates fills"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "[回测、实盘与优化](06-backtest-live-optimization.md)"
msgstr ""
"[Backtesting, Live Trading, and Optimization](06-backtest-live-"
"optimization.md)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**Optimizer**"
msgstr "**Optimizer**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "优化器，在参数空间搜索并多次回测，汇总目标函数"
msgstr ""
"Optimizer: searches the parameter space and runs backtests multiple times, "
"aggregating the objective function"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**Trader**"
msgstr "**Trader**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "实盘交易管理，按 schedule 触发 Operator 并协调 Broker"
msgstr ""
"Live trading management: triggers the Operator according to schedule and "
"coordinates the Broker"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**Broker**"
msgstr "**Broker**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "订单执行与成交回报的接口抽象"
msgstr "Abstract interface for order execution and fill reports"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**config**"
msgstr "**config**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "运行配置（资产池、区间、成本、资金计划等），回测/实盘/优化共用"
msgstr ""
"Run configuration (asset pool, time range, costs, capital plan, etc.), shared "
"by backtesting/live trading/optimization"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**qt.run**"
msgstr "**qt.run**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid ""
"统一入口：qt.run(op, mode=..., **kwargs) → op.run(config, datasource, logger)"
msgstr ""
"Unified entry point: qt.run(op, mode=..., **kwargs) → op.run(config, "
"datasource, logger)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:34
msgid "2. dtype_id 的构成与示例"
msgstr "2. Composition and examples of dtype_id"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:36
msgid "dtype_id 由三部分拼接而成：**name_assettype_freq**。"
msgstr ""
"dtype_id is composed of three parts concatenated together: "
"**name_assettype_freq**."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:38
msgid "**name**：数据类型名称（如 close、open、total_mv、pe）。"
msgstr "**name**: data type name (e.g., close, open, total_mv, pe)."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:39
msgid "**assettype**：资产类型，如 `E`（股票）、`IDX`（指数）、`ANY`（任意）。"
msgstr ""
"**assettype**: asset type, such as `E` (stocks), `IDX` (index), `ANY` (any)."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:40
msgid "**freq**：数据频率，如 `d`（日）、`w`（周）、`m`（月）、`q`（季）。"
msgstr ""
"**freq**: data frequency, e.g., `d` (daily), `w` (weekly), `m` (monthly), `q` "
"(quarterly)."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:42
msgid "示例："
msgstr "Example:"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "dtype_id"
msgstr "dtype_id"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "`close_E_d`"
msgstr "`close_E_d`"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "股票日频收盘价"
msgstr "Daily closing price of stocks"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "`close_IDX_d`"
msgstr "`close_IDX_d`"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "指数日频收盘价"
msgstr "Daily closing price of an index"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "`close_ANY_d`"
msgstr "`close_ANY_d`"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "任意资产日频收盘价"
msgstr "Daily closing price of any asset"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "`total_mv_E_q`"
msgstr "`total_mv_E_q`"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "股票季频总市值"
msgstr "Quarterly total market capitalization of stocks"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "`pe_E_d`"
msgstr "`pe_E_d`"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "股票日频市盈率（若存在）"
msgstr "Daily stock P/E ratio (if available)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:52
msgid ""
"策略在 `get_data(dtype_id)` 时使用的 id 需与策略声明的 DataType 所生成的 "
"dtype_id 一致（通常可通过策略的 `data_type_ids` 属性查看）。"
msgstr ""
"When the strategy calls `get_data(dtype_id)`, the id used must match the "
"dtype_id generated by the DataType declared by the strategy (usually viewable "
"via the strategy’s `data_type_ids` property)."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:54
msgid "3. 三种信号类型 PT/PS/VS 的语义对比表"
msgstr "3. Semantic comparison table of the three signal types: PT/PS/VS"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "类型"
msgstr "Type"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "全称"
msgstr "Full name"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "含义（一句话）"
msgstr "Meaning (one sentence)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "示例"
msgstr "Example"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**PT**"
msgstr "**PT**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "Position Target"
msgstr "Position Target"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "目标持仓比例，信号表示希望达到的多空仓位比例"
msgstr ""
"Target position ratio: the signal indicates the desired long/short position "
"ratio to reach."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "0.5 表示目标 50% 多头仓位"
msgstr "0.5 indicates a target 50% long position."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**PS**"
msgstr "**PS**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "Proportion Signal"
msgstr "Proportion Signal"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "比例买卖，信号表示用资金或持仓的多少比例买入/卖出"
msgstr ""
"Proportional trading: the signal indicates what proportion of capital or "
"holdings to buy/sell."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "0.5 表示用 50% 资金买入或卖出 50% 持仓"
msgstr ""
"0.5 indicates using 50% of capital to buy, or selling 50% of the position."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**VS**"
msgstr "**VS**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "Volume Signal"
msgstr "Volume Signal"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "数量买卖，信号表示买入/卖出的数量（股或份）"
msgstr ""
"Quantity-based trading: the signal indicates the quantity to buy/sell (shares "
"or units)."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "100 表示买入 100 股，-50 表示卖出 50 股"
msgstr "100 indicates buying 100 shares; -50 indicates selling 50 shares."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:62
msgid ""
"同一数值在不同 signal_type 下会被解析为不同的委托意图；Group 的 signal_type 在"
"添加策略时确定，同组内策略输出同一类型信号再由 blender 混合。"
msgstr ""
"The same numeric value will be interpreted as different order intents under "
"different signal_type; a Group’s signal_type is determined when adding the "
"strategy, and strategies within the same group output the same type of "
"signal, which is then blended by the blender."

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:64
msgid "4. 三种策略基类的输入/输出对比表"
msgstr "4. Comparison table of inputs/outputs for three strategy base classes"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "基类"
msgstr "Base class"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "典型用途"
msgstr "Typical use cases"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "输入（get_data 等）"
msgstr "Inputs (get_data, etc.)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "输出（realize 返回值）"
msgstr "Outputs (return value of realize)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**RuleIterator**"
msgstr "**RuleIterator**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "择时、单规则迭代"
msgstr "Market timing, single-rule iteration"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "单资产或多资产的数据窗口（按 dtype_id）"
msgstr "Single-asset or multi-asset data window (by dtype_id)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "标量信号（如 1 / -1 / 0），同一规则作用于所有资产"
msgstr "Scalar signal (e.g., 1 / -1 / 0); the same rule applies to all assets"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**FactorSorter**"
msgstr "**FactorSorter**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "因子选股"
msgstr "Factor-based stock selection"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "多资产截面数据（如多只股票的因子值）"
msgstr ""
"Multi-asset cross-sectional data (e.g., factor values for multiple stocks)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "一维因子数组（每资产一个值），引擎按因子排序与筛选规则选股"
msgstr ""
"1D factor array (one value per asset); the engine selects stocks by factor "
"ranking and filtering rules"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "**GeneralStg**"
msgstr "**GeneralStg**"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "通用多资产策略"
msgstr "General-purpose multi-asset strategy"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "多资产、多数据类型的数据窗口"
msgstr "Multi-asset, multi-data-type data window"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md
msgid "一维信号数组（每资产一个目标仓位或买卖比例）"
msgstr "1D signal array (one target position or buy/sell ratio per asset)"

#: ../../source/design/01-concepts.md:72
msgid ""
"更多细节见 [Strategy 如何运行：时机、数据与参数](05-strategy-lifecycle.md)。"
msgstr ""
"For more details, see [How Strategy Runs: Timing, Data, and Parameters](05-"
"strategy-lifecycle.md)."
